            <abstract id="ref34" label="Abstract">This collection details experience of Donald G. Martin as he served in World War II and Korean War with U.S. Navy and U.S. Marine Corps respectively. The collection contains video of an oral history interview, and photographs taken during Korean War.</abstract>
